00:01:02.000 --> 00:01:07.000
we can immediately it to a block on four springs but as we just argued,

00:01:07.000 --> 00:01:12.000
these four springs are actually equivalent to one spring with a spring constant of 4K,

00:01:12.000 --> 00:01:17.000
so we can actually replace this K with 4K and now we can use this equation.

00:01:17.000 --> 00:01:21.000
And plugging in our numbers here, we find that the period of the oscillation of the car

